title: Bitcoin Fog coin mixer operator Roman Sterlingov found guilty in jury trial
description:
Roman Sterlingov has been found guilty by a jury on all charges related to the Bitcoin Fog coin mixer, according to a US Department of Justice press release. Sterlingov was charged with guilty of conspiracy, sting money laundering, operating an unlicensed money-transmitting business, and violations of the DC Money Transmitters Act.
